        }
        lines {
          text: "3. **One-Tap Prune**: A visible \"Clear Boosted Tracks\" banner at the top of the queue that instantly restores the playlist to its pristine, original state.`"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "  },"
