          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "                  In its current raw state, it behaves like a **student concept**. Spotify features are designed to be extremely quiet. The original design uses disruptive modal alerts (which Spotify hasn\'t used for core functions in half a decade) and breaks the \"Queue Sovereignty\" rule (the concept that a user\'s active play queue is holy ground that should never be modified without clear permission and visibility)."
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
