  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Bold Typography\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Bold Typography\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-[#090909] text-white font-sans overflow-hidden flex flex-col relative\\\">\\n  <style>\\n    .spotify-gradient {\\n      background: radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, #1DB95433 0%, transparent 50%),\\n                  radial-gradient(circle at 20% 80%, #191414 0%, #090909 100%);\\n    }\\n    .glass-panel {\\n      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);\\n      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\\n      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\\n    }\\n    .text-display {\\n      letter-spacing: -0.04em;\\n      line-height: 0.9;\\n    }\\n    .annotation-pin {\\n      width: 24px;\\n      height: 24px;\\n      background: #1DB954;\\n      color: black;\\n      font-weight: bold;\\n      border-radius: 50%;\\n      display: flex;\\n      align-items: center;\\n      justify-content: center;\\n      box-shadow: 0 0 15px #1DB95466;\\n      font-size: 12px;\\n      cursor: pointer;\\n    }\\n  </style>\\n\\n  <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 spotify-gradient\\\"></div>\\n\\n  <!-- Top Navigation Bar -->\\n  <nav class=\\\"h-16 flex items-center px-8 z-10\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-4\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center\\\">\342\200\271</div>\\n      <div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center opacity-50\\\">\342\200\272</div>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"ml-auto flex items-center gap-6\\\">\\n      <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-zinc-400\\\">PM REVIEW MODE</span>\\n      <div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-zinc-800 border border-white/20\\\"></div>\\n    </div>\\n  </nav>\\n\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex gap-8 px-8 pb-8 z-10\\\">\\n    <!-- Left: Currently Playing (The \'Hero\') -->\\n    <div class=\\\"w-1/3 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"relative group\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"aspect-square w-full bg-zinc-800 rounded-xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden relative\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute bottom-4 left-4\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-zinc-300 uppercase tracking-tighter mb-1\\\">Now Playing</p>\\n            <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold\\\">Midnight City</h3>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-zinc-400\\\">M83 \342\200\242 Hurry Up, We\'re Dreaming</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute -top-2 -right-2 annotation-pin\\\">A</div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- The Improved Interaction Trigger Overlay -->\\n      <div class=\\\"glass-panel p-6 rounded-2xl relative\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute -top-3 -left-3 annotation-pin\\\">B</div>\\n        <h2 class=\\\"text-3xl font-black text-display mb-4 italic\\\">BREAK THE LOOP?</h2>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-sm text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-6\\\">\\n          Our systems detect you\'ve been circling the same 12 tracks for 4 days. Ready for a curated expansion based on your M83 vibe?\\n        </p>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex gap-3\\\">\\n          <button class=\\\"flex-1 bg-white text-black font-bold py-3 rounded-full text-sm\\\">Boost Queue</button>\\n          <button class=\\\"px-4 bg-white/10 text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-full text-sm\\\">Not Now</button>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Right: The Queue & Insights Panel -->\\n    <div class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-end mb-6\\\">\\n        <h1 class=\\\"text-6xl font-black text-display uppercase\\\">Boosted Queue</h1>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Target Metric</p>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-lg font-mono text-[#1DB954]\\\">Boost Conv. +12.4%</p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 glass-panel rounded-2xl p-6 flex flex-col gap-4 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n        <!-- List Headers -->\\n        <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-12 text-[10px] font-bold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-white/5 pb-2\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"col-span-6\\\">Title</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"col-span-3\\\">Reasoning</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"col-span-3 text-right\\\">Signal Strength</div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Queue Items -->\\n        <div class=\\\"flex flex-col gap-1\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-12 items-center py-2 px-3 bg-white/5 rounded-lg border border-white/10 group\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"col-span-6 flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-zinc-700 rounded\\\"></div>\\n              <div>\\n                <p class=\\\"text-sm font-bold\\\">Wait</p>\\n                <p class=\\\"text-xs text-zinc-400\\\">M83</p>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"col-span-3 text-[10px] text-zinc-400\\\">Original Loop</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"col-span-3 flex justify-end gap-1\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-1 h-3 bg-zinc-600\\\"></div>\\n              <div class=\\\"w-1 h-3 bg-zinc-600\\\"></div>\\n              <div class=\\\"w-1 h-3 bg-zinc-600\\\"></div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-12 items-center py-2 px-3 border border-[#1DB954]/30 bg-[#1DB954]/10 rounded-lg relative\\\">\\n             <div class=\\\"absolute -left-6 annotation-pin bg-orange-500\\\">C</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"col-span-6 flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-[#1DB954]/20 rounded flex items-center justify-center text-[#1DB954]\\\">\342\232\241</div>\\n              <div>\\n                <p class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-[#1DB954]\\\">Genesis <span class=\\\"ml-2 text-[10px] border border-[#1DB954] px-1 rounded\\\">BOOSTED</span></p>\\n                <p class=\\\"text-xs text-zinc-400\\\">Grimes</p>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"col-span-3 text-[10px] text-white/60 font-medium italic\\\">Matches \'Midnight City\' synth profile</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"col-span-3 flex justify-end gap-1\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-1 h-3 bg-[#1DB954]\\\"></div>\\n              <div class=\\\"w-1 h-3 bg-[#1DB954]\\\"></div>\\n              <div class=\\\"w-1 h-3 bg-[#1DB954]\\\"></div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-12 items-center py-2 px-3 border border-[#1DB954]/30 bg-[#1DB954]/10 rounded-lg\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"col-span-6 flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-[#1DB954]/20 rounded flex items-center justify-center text-[#1DB954]\\\">\342\232\241</div>\\n              <div>\\n                <p class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-[#1DB954]\\\">Lower Your Eyelids... <span class=\\\"ml-2 text-[10px] border border-[#1DB954] px-1 rounded\\\">BOOSTED</span></p>\\n                <p class=\\\"text-xs text-zinc-400\\\">M83</p>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"col-span-3 text-[10px] text-white/60 font-medium italic\\\">Deep cut from artist in loop</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"col-span-3 flex justify-end gap-1\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-1 h-3 bg-[#1DB954]\\\"></div>\\n              <div class=\\\"w-1 h-3 bg-zinc-600\\\"></div>\\n              <div class=\\\"w-1 h-3 bg-zinc-600\\\"></div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Annotation Sidebar Legend -->\\n        <div class=\\\"mt-auto bg-black/40 border border-white/10 p-4 rounded-xl\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-zinc-500 mb-2 tracking-widest\\\">SENIOR PM / UX NOTES</p>\\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex gap-3 items-start\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] bg-[#1DB954] text-black px-1.5 rounded font-bold mt-0.5\\\">A</span>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-zinc-300\\\"><strong class=\\\"text-white\\\">Contextual Trust:</strong> Showing why songs are added prevents \\\"WTF\\\" moments in the queue.</p>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex gap-3 items-start\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] bg-[#1DB954] text-black px-1.5 rounded font-bold mt-0.5\\\">B</span>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-zinc-300\\\"><strong class=\\\"text-white\\\">Microcopy:</strong> Shifted from passive \\\"Want to?\\\" to active \\\"Break the loop?\\\" to tap into FOMO.</p>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex gap-3 items-start\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] bg-orange-500 text-black px-1.5 rounded font-bold mt-0.5\\\">C</span>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-zinc-300\\\"><strong class=\\\"text-white\\\">Friction:</strong> Users can instantly swipe to remove boosted songs, maintaining control over their curation.</p>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </main>\\n\\n  <!-- Player Controls (Static) -->\\n  <footer class=\\\"h-24 bg-black border-t border-white/5 flex items-center px-8 z-10\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"w-1/3 flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n       <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-zinc-800 rounded\\\"></div>\\n       <div>\\n         <p class=\\\"text-sm font-bold\\\">Midnight City</p>\\n         <p class=\\\"text-xs text-zinc-400\\\">M83</p>\\n       </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"w-1/3 flex flex-col items-center gap-2\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-6 opacity-80\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-lg\\\">shuffle</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-lg\\\">previous</span>\\n        <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-black\\\">\342\226\266</div>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-lg\\\">next</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-lg\\\">repeat</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"w-full max-w-md h-1 bg-zinc-800 rounded-full overflow-hidden\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"w-1/3 h-full bg-white\\\"></div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"w-1/3 flex justify-end gap-4 items-center opacity-60\\\">\\n      <span>Lyrics</span>\\n      <span>Queue</span>\\n      <span>Devices</span>\\n      <div class=\\\"w-24 h-1 bg-zinc-800 rounded-full\\\"></div>\\n    </div>\\n  </footer>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Bold Typography\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Bold Typography\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-[#090909] text-white font-sans overflow-hidden flex flex-col relative\\\">\\n  <style>\\n    .spotify-gradient {\\n      background: radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, #1DB95433 0%, transparent 50%),\\n                  radial-gradient(circle at 20% 80%, #191414 0%, #090909 100%);\\n    }\\n    .glass-panel {\\n      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);\\n      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\\n      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\\n    }\\n    .text-display {\\n      letter-spacing: -0.04em;\\n      line-height: 0.9;\\n    }\\n    .annotation-pin {\\n      width: 24px;\\n      height: 24px;\\n      background: #1DB954;\\n      color: black;\\n      font-weight: bold;\\n      border-radius: 50%;\\n      display: flex;\\n      align-items: center;\\n      justify-content: center;\\n      box-shadow: 0 0 15px #1DB95466;\\n      font-size: 12px;\\n      cursor: pointer;\\n    }\\n  </style>\\n\\n  <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 spotify-gradient\\\"></div>\\n\\n  <!-- Top Navigation Bar -->\\n  <nav class=\\\"h-16 flex items-center px-8 z-10\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-4\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center\\\">\342\200\271</div>\\n      <div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center opacity-50\\\">\342\200\272</div>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"ml-auto flex items-center gap-6\\\">\\n      <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-zinc-400\\\">PM REVIEW MODE</span>\\n      <div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-zinc-800 border border-white/20\\\"></div>\\n    </div>\\n  </nav>\\n\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex gap-8 px-8 pb-8 z-10\\\">\\n    <!-- Left: Currently Playing (The \'Hero\') -->\\n    <div class=\\\"w-1/3 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"relative group\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"aspect-square w-full bg-zinc-800 rounded-xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden relative\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute bottom-4 left-4\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-zinc-300 uppercase tracking-tighter mb-1\\\">Now Playing</p>\\n            <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold\\\">Midnight City</h3>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-zinc-400\\\">M83 \342\200\242 Hurry Up, We\'re Dreaming</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute -top-2 -right-2 annotation-pin\\\">A</div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- The Improved Interaction Trigger Overlay -->\\n      <div class=\\\"glass-panel p-6 rounded-2xl relative\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute -top-3 -left-3 annotation-pin\\\">B</div>\\n        <h2 class=\\\"text-3xl font-black text-display mb-4 italic\\\">BREAK THE LOOP?</h2>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-sm text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-6\\\">\\n          Our systems detect you\'ve been circling the same 12 tracks for 4 days. Ready for a curated expansion based on your M83 vibe?\\n        </p>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex gap-3\\\">\\n          <button class=\\\"flex-1 bg-white text-black font-bold py-3 rounded-full text-sm\\\">Boost Queue</button>\\n          <button class=\\\"px-4 bg-white/10 text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-full text-sm\\\">Not Now</button>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Right: The Queue & Insights Panel -->\\n    <div class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-end mb-6\\\">\\n        <h1 class=\\\"text-6xl font-black text-display uppercase\\\">Boosted Queue</h1>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Target Metric</p>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-lg font-mono text-[#1DB954]\\\">Boost Conv. +12.4%</p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 glass-panel rounded-2xl p-6 flex flex-col gap-4 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n        <!-- List Headers -->\\n        <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-12 text-[10px] font-bold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-white/5 pb-2\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"col-span-6\\\">Title</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"col-span-3\\\">Reasoning</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"col-span-3 text-right\\\">Signal Strength</div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Queue Items -->\\n        <div class=\\\"flex flex-col gap-1\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-12 items-center py-2 px-3 bg-white/5 rounded-lg border border-white/10 group\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"col-span-6 flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-zinc-700 rounded\\\"></div>\\n              <div>\\n                <p class=\\\"text-sm font-bold\\\">Wait</p>\\n                <p class=\\\"text-xs text-zinc-400\\\">M83</p>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"col-span-3 text-[10px] text-zinc-400\\\">Original Loop</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"col-span-3 flex justify-end gap-1\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-1 h-3 bg-zinc-600\\\"></div>\\n              <div class=\\\"w-1 h-3 bg-zinc-600\\\"></div>\\n              <div class=\\\"w-1 h-3 bg-zinc-600\\\"></div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-12 items-center py-2 px-3 border border-[#1DB954]/30 bg-[#1DB954]/10 rounded-lg relative\\\">\\n             <div class=\\\"absolute -left-6 annotation-pin bg-orange-500\\\">C</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"col-span-6 flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-[#1DB954]/20 rounded flex items-center justify-center text-[#1DB954]\\\">\342\232\241</div>\\n              <div>\\n                <p class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-[#1DB954]\\\">Genesis <span class=\\\"ml-2 text-[10px] border border-[#1DB954] px-1 rounded\\\">BOOSTED</span></p>\\n                <p class=\\\"text-xs text-zinc-400\\\">Grimes</p>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"col-span-3 text-[10px] text-white/60 font-medium italic\\\">Matches \'Midnight City\' synth profile</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"col-span-3 flex justify-end gap-1\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-1 h-3 bg-[#1DB954]\\\"></div>\\n              <div class=\\\"w-1 h-3 bg-[#1DB954]\\\"></div>\\n              <div class=\\\"w-1 h-3 bg-[#1DB954]\\\"></div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-12 items-center py-2 px-3 border border-[#1DB954]/30 bg-[#1DB954]/10 rounded-lg\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"col-span-6 flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-[#1DB954]/20 rounded flex items-center justify-center text-[#1DB954]\\\">\342\232\241</div>\\n              <div>\\n                <p class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-[#1DB954]\\\">Lower Your Eyelids... <span class=\\\"ml-2 text-[10px] border border-[#1DB954] px-1 rounded\\\">BOOSTED</span></p>\\n                <p class=\\\"text-xs text-zinc-400\\\">M83</p>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"col-span-3 text-[10px] text-white/60 font-medium italic\\\">Deep cut from artist in loop</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"col-span-3 flex justify-end gap-1\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-1 h-3 bg-[#1DB954]\\\"></div>\\n              <div class=\\\"w-1 h-3 bg-zinc-600\\\"></div>\\n              <div class=\\\"w-1 h-3 bg-zinc-600\\\"></div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Annotation Sidebar Legend -->\\n        <div class=\\\"mt-auto bg-black/40 border border-white/10 p-4 rounded-xl\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-zinc-500 mb-2 tracking-widest\\\">SENIOR PM / UX NOTES</p>\\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex gap-3 items-start\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] bg-[#1DB954] text-black px-1.5 rounded font-bold mt-0.5\\\">A</span>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-zinc-300\\\"><strong class=\\\"text-white\\\">Contextual Trust:</strong> Showing why songs are added prevents \\\"WTF\\\" moments in the queue.</p>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex gap-3 items-start\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] bg-[#1DB954] text-black px-1.5 rounded font-bold mt-0.5\\\">B</span>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-zinc-300\\\"><strong class=\\\"text-white\\\">Microcopy:</strong> Shifted from passive \\\"Want to?\\\" to active \\\"Break the loop?\\\" to tap into FOMO.</p>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex gap-3 items-start\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] bg-orange-500 text-black px-1.5 rounded font-bold mt-0.5\\\">C</span>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-zinc-300\\\"><strong class=\\\"text-white\\\">Friction:</strong> Users can instantly swipe to remove boosted songs, maintaining control over their curation.</p>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </main>\\n\\n  <!-- Player Controls (Static) -->\\n  <footer class=\\\"h-24 bg-black border-t border-white/5 flex items-center px-8 z-10\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"w-1/3 flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n       <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-zinc-800 rounded\\\"></div>\\n       <div>\\n         <p class=\\\"text-sm font-bold\\\">Midnight City</p>\\n         <p class=\\\"text-xs text-zinc-400\\\">M83</p>\\n       </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"w-1/3 flex flex-col items-center gap-2\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-6 opacity-80\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-lg\\\">shuffle</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-lg\\\">previous</span>\\n        <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-black\\\">\342\226\266</div>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-lg\\\">next</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-lg\\\">repeat</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"w-full max-w-md h-1 bg-zinc-800 rounded-full overflow-hidden\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"w-1/3 h-full bg-white\\\"></div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"w-1/3 flex justify-end gap-4 items-center opacity-60\\\">\\n      <span>Lyrics</span>\\n      <span>Queue</span>\\n      <span>Devices</span>\\n      <div class=\\\"w-24 h-1 bg-zinc-800 rounded-full\\\"></div>\\n    </div>\\n  </footer>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
