d component. I\'m also eliminating the grid layout within the `main` element in `src/App.tsx`. The goal is a simpler, more focused layout centered around the `SpotifyPrototype`. I\'ll be adjusting the flex properties of the main container and the `SpotifyPrototype` to achieve this.\n\n\n**Refactoring for Simplicity**\n\nI\'m now simplifying the `App.tsx` layout using a flexbox container, removing the grid. I\'ve centered the `SpotifyPrototype` and the instructions bubble. I am using `max-w-lg` for width control. The instructions are now elegantly placed. The goal is a clean, centered interface.\n\n\n"
